@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="custom-margin-top">
    <div class="container py-5 ">
        <!-- Title -->
        <h1 class="display4 textcolor">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

       <!-- Section 1: Privacy and Data Protection -->
<h2 class="display4 privacymargintopcolored">1. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
<p class="paracolor">
    At Vacation Destination, your privacy is our priority. We do not collect any personal data, such as names, contact details, or payment information. Here’s how we handle data to provide a secure and customized experience.
</p>
<br />

<!-- Subsection 1.1: Non-Personal Data -->
<h6 class="margintop privacytextcolor">1.1 Non-Personal Data</h6>
<ul class="privacyparacolor">
    <li>
        <strong>What We Collect:</strong> We gather non-personal data, including general usage patterns (e.g., pages visited, device type, and browsing duration).
    </li>
    <br />
    <li>
        <strong>How We Use It:</strong> This information is used in an anonymized form to enhance our website’s performance, improve user experience, and understand how our services are being used.
    </li>
</ul>
<br />

<!-- Subsection 1.2: Cookies and Tracking Technologies -->
<h3 class="margintop privacytextcolor">1.2 Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h3>
<ul class="privacyparacolor">
    <li>
        <strong>Purpose of Cookies:</strong> Cookies are small files stored on your device to support essential functions, improve performance, and remember your preferences.
    </li>
    <br />
    <li>
        <strong>Types of Cookies We Use:</strong>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> Required for core functions, such as navigating the site.</li>
            <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> Track site usage to help us enhance functionality and loading speed.</li>
            <li><strong>Preference Cookies:</strong> Store settings like language choice to personalize your experience.</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <br />
    <li>
        <strong>Cookie Management:</strong> You may control cookie settings in your browser to accept, block, or delete cookies. We employ secure technologies and follow data protection best practices to manage and anonymize all collected data.
    </li>
</ul>
<br />

<!-- Section 2: Policy Updates -->
<h2 class="display4 privacymargintopcolored">2. Policy Updates</h2>
<p class="paracolor">
    We may update these policies periodically on this page to improve our service. We encourage you to review it from time to time.
</p>
<br />

<!-- Section 3: Contact Us -->
<h2 class="display4 privacymargintopcolored">3. Contact Us</h2>
<p class="paracolor">
    If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at: 
    <a href="mailto:support@vacationdestination.com" class="text-decoration-none">support@vacationdestination.com</a>
</p>
<br />

